<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>VPN sitio a sitio con IPsec Fortinet on Atlas</title><link>https://www.javiercd.es/posts/vpn/site_to_site_fortinet/</link><description>Recent content in VPN sitio a sitio con IPsec Fortinet on Atlas</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>es</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 10:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.javiercd.es/posts/vpn/site_to_site_fortinet/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>VPN sitio a sitio con IPsec Fortinet</title><link>https://www.javiercd.es/posts/vpn/site_to_site_fortinet/site_to_site_fortinet/</link><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 10:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.javiercd.es/posts/vpn/site_to_site_fortinet/site_to_site_fortinet/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;En este post voy a montar una VPN IPSEC usando cortafuegos Fortinet , para ello los visualizaré en GNS3 .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://www.javiercd.es/vpn/site_to_site_fortinet/img/Pastedimage20240330235321.png" alt=""&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="preparación-del-escenario"&gt;Preparación del escenario&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Para crear la VPN añadiré al escenario un nuevo Fortigate .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Así que vamos a proceder a configurarlo , lo primero sera conocer la IP que le ha dado el DHCP :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;FortiGate-VM64-KVM login: admin
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Password:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;You are forced to change your password. Please input a new password.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;New Password:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Confirm Password:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Welcome!
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;FortiGate-VM64-KVM &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# get system interface physical port1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;onboard&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;==[&lt;/span&gt;port1&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; mode: dhcp
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; ip: 192.168.122.22 255.255.255.0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; ipv6: ::/0
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; status: up
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; speed: 1000Mbps &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;Duplex: full&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; FEC: none
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; FEC_cap: none
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Esta IP que me ha dado por DHCP se la configurare como estática .&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>